Class AbstractAssertion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soa.policy.wspolicy.AbstractAssertion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assertion
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSubPolicyAssertion

    public abstract class AbstractAssertion
extends java.lang.Object
implements Assertion
    A base class for Assertions, providing the initial implementation of the Assertion interface. Both the optional attribute and the ignorable attribute default to false.
